====Teotihuacano====
{{Disputed|section|date=February 2010}}
[[Teotihuacan]] was a city built around a cave held sacred to those who built it- while their identity is disputed, what is know is that around the 1st century CE the rulers of Teotihuacan began a massive urbanization campaign, building temple complexes and homes laid out on a grid that eventually encompassed 30&nbsp;km<U+00B2> (over 11<U+00BD> square miles).<!-- (Add more about masks) -->

