====Classic Veracruz Culture====

{{Main|Remojadas|Classic Veracruz Culture#Ceramics}}

In his 1957 book on Mesoamerican art, [[Miguel Covarrubias]] speaks of Remojadas' "magnificent hollow figures with expressive faces, in majestic postures and wearing elaborate paraphernalia indicated by added clay elements."<ref>Covarrubias, p. 193.</ref><br>
<gallery widths="200px" heights="180px" perrow="3">
