</gallery>

====Maya====

{{Main|Maya art|Maya ceramics|Maya architecture}}
The [[Maya civilization]] occupied the south of [[Mexico]], all of [[Guatemala]] and [[Belize]], and the western portions of [[Honduras]] and [[El Salvador]].
<gallery widths="170px" heights="170px" perrow="4">
Image:Bonampak painting+contrast.jpg|<center>Fresco from Structure I, [[Bonampak]], Chiapas, 790 CE
